Revision history for Log-Any-For-LWP

0.06    2015-08-17 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- Switch from Log::Any to Log::Any::IfLOG.


0.05     2013-04-10 (SHARYANTO)

         - Pass -decode_response_body to LWP::UserAgent::Patch::LogResponse.


0.04     2013-04-10 (SHARYANTO)

         [INCOMPATIBLE CHANGES]

         - Split -log_request config into -log_request_header (default 1) and
           -log_request_body (default 0).

         [ENHANCEMENTS]

         - Use LWP::UserAgent::Patch::LogRequestContent.


0.03     2012-08-23 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Update patch module names.


0.02     2012-07-17 (SHARYANTO)

         - No functional changes. Fix example in Synopsis.


0.01     2012-07-17 (SHARYANTO)

         - First release.
